# Social Icons (SVG)

Fallback social icons if needed.
The SocialIconLinks component includes built-in SVG icons for:
- linkedin.svg
- instagram.svg
- pinterest.svg
- tiktok.svg
- spotify.svg
- bluesky.svg
- threads.svg
- x.svg
- github.svg
- youtube.svg
- email.svg

These are embedded in the component, so separate files are optional.
